ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert icmp $EXTERNAL_NET any -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"PROTOCOL-ICMP Destination Unreachable Network Unreachable"; icode:0; itype:3; metadata:ruleset community; classtype:misc-activity; sid:401; rev:9; )

ids_alerts.rule_msg: SURICATA HTTP request field missing colon

ids_alerts.rule_msg: SURICATA Applayer Detect protocol only one direction
